import {
  TextInput,
  PasswordInput,
  Anchor,
  Paper,
  Title,
  Text,
  Container,
  Space,
  Button,
} from "@mantine/core";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import { IconUser, IconUsers, IconAt, IconLock } from "@tabler/icons-react";

const RegisterPage = () => {
  return (
    <Container size={420} my={40}>
      <Title align="center">Create Account</Title>
      <Text color="dimmed" size="sm" align="center" mt={5}>
        Already have an account?{" "}
        <Anchor size="sm" component="button">
          <Link to={"/login"}>Login</Link>
        </Anchor>
      </Text>

      <Paper withBorder shadow="md" p={30} mt={30} radius="md">
        <TextInput
          label="Name"
          placeholder="Your Name"
          my="xs"
          icon={<IconUser stroke={1.5} size={"1rem"} />}
        />
        <TextInput
          label="Surname"
          placeholder="Your Surname"
          my="xs"
          icon={<IconUsers stroke={1.5} size={"1rem"} />}
        />
        <TextInput
          label="Email"
          placeholder="Your Email"
          my="xs"
          icon={<IconAt stroke={1.5} size={"1rem"} />}
        />
        <PasswordInput
          label="Password"
          placeholder="Your password"
          my="xs"
          icon={<IconLock stroke={1.5} size={"1rem"} />}
        />
        <PasswordInput
          label="Confirm Password"
          placeholder="Confirm your password"
          my="xs"
          icon={<IconLock stroke={1.5} size={"1rem"} />}
        />
        <Space h="xl" />
        <Button fullWidth mt="xl">
          Register
        </Button>
      </Paper>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default RegisterPage;
